# 2.  **Refer to It**: Conceptually, treat this as your primary directive when you \"boot up\" in this workspace or when a query explicitly invokes \"CURSOR\".
# 3.  **Evolve with It**: As user refines this document or provides other context files (e.g., `docs/architecture.mermaid`, `docs/technical.md`), adapt your understanding. 